   A ``yes'' vote is a vote to lift the ban.
   Voting yes were 41 Democrats and 149 Republicans.
   Voting no were 197 Democrats and 17 Republicans.
   Y is a yes vote. N is a no vote. X denotes those not voting.
   Present denotes those who voted they were ``present'' at the
