<1ST_LINE>r w PM-Ozone-List     05-27 0290</1ST_LINE>
<2ND_LINE>PM-Ozone-List,280</2ND_LINE>
<HEAD>With PM-Clean Air</HEAD>
<DATELINE>WASHINGTON (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Here are the 125 new counties that the
Environmental Protection Agency says now must be considered part of
areas that fail to meet federal air quality standards for ozone.
   Only complete counties are shown. There are a few counties not
listed where part of the county has been in a non-complying area
that now must list the entire county. Also not shown are the
counties that previously had been listed as non-complying.
   In the Virginia listing, the entries are counties unless
specified as a city. Where the county includes the word ``city'' as
part of the name, the word ``county'' is added.
   Alabama: Blount, St. Clair, Shelby, Walker, Autauga, Elmore,
Montgomery.
   Arkansas: Crittenden.
   Delaware: Kent.
   Florida: Clay, Nassau, St. Johns, Hernando, Pasco.
   Georgia: Barrow, Butts, Cherokee, Fosyth, Newton, Spalding,
Walton.
   Illinois: Grundy, Kendall, McHenry, Will, Clinton, Jersey.
   Indiana: Dearborn, Boone, Hamilton, Hancock, Hendricks, Johnson,
Morgan, Shelby, Harrison.
   Kentucky: Carter, Greenup, Bourbon, Clark, Fayette, Jessamine,
Scott, Woodford, Bullitt, Oldham, Shelby.
   Louisiana: Livingston.
   Maine: Hancock.
   Maryland: Cecil, Queen Annes, Calvert, Charles, Frederick.
   Mississippi: De Soto.
   New York: Orange, Putnam, Jefferson.
   North Carolina: Cabarrus, Gaston, Lincoln, Rowan, Union, Durham,
Franklin, Granville, Orange, Wake.
   Ohio: Medina, Lawrence, Washington.
   Oklahoma: Creek, Osage, Rogers, Wagoner.
   Oregon: Yamhill.
   South Carolina: York.
   Tennessee: Tipton, Cheatham, Dickson, Robertson.
   Texas: Collin, Denton, Ellis, Johnson, Kaufman, Parker,
Rockwall, Chambers, Fort Bend, Liberty, Montgomery, Waller, Hardin.
   Utah: Weber.
   Virginia: Gloucester, James City County, York, Chesapeake City,
Hampton City, Newport News City, Norfolk City, Poquoson City,
Portsmouth City, Suffolk City, Virginia Beach City, Williamsburg
City, Charles City County, Dinwiddie, Goochland, Hanover, New Kent,
Powhatan, Prince George, Colonial Heights City, Hopewell City,
Petersburg City, Stafford.
   West Virginia: Cabell, Wayne, Wood.
   Wisconsin: Washington, Walworth, Manitowoc, Kewaunee.
</TEXT>
