   New York: Orange, Putnam, Rockland, Suffolk, Madison, Oswego.
   North Carolina: Durham, Franklin, Orange, Wake.
   Ohio: Geauga, Lake, Lorain, Medina, Portage, Summit, Jefferson.
   Oklahoma: Canadian, Cleveland, Logan, McClain, Oklahoma,
Pottawatomie.
   Oregon: Clackamas, Washington, Yamhill.
   Pennsylvania: Beaver, Fayette, Washington, Westmoreland.
   Tennessee: Tipton, Cheatham, Dickson, Robertson, Rutherford,
Sumner, Williamson, Wilson.
   Texas: Brazoria, Ford Bend, Galveston, Harris, Liberty,
Montgomery, Waller.
   Utah: Davis.
   Virginia: Fairfax, Loudoun, Prince William, Stafford, Fairfax
City, Falls Church City, Manassas Park City, Manassas City.
   Washington: Clark, Snohomish.
   West Virginia: Brooke, Hancock.
   Wisconsin: Douglas, St. Croix.
