<HEAD>Reagan Declines to Discuss Options for Ousting Noriega</HEAD>
<DATELINE>HELSINKI, Finland (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   President Reagan said Friday that he
and his advisers have not had a chance to discuss new American
moves in the drive to pressure Panamanian ruler Gen. Manuel Antonio
Noriega out of power.
   ``We have had no opportunity to consider where we go'' from
