<HEAD>Reuters Buys A 48.8 Percent Stake in Australian Associated Press</HEAD>
<DATELINE>LONDON (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Reuters Holdings PLC said Friday it acquired a
48.8 percent stake in Australian Associated Press Pty. Ltd. for
30.8 million pounds, or around $57 million.
   The agreement gives Reuters and publisher Rupert Murdoch's
Australian-based News Corp. equal stakes in Australian Associated
Press, Reuters said.
