Australian newspapers.
   Reuters said it acquired 44.65 percent of Australian Associated
Press from companies within John Fairfax Ltd., an Australian
publishing group, and 4.15 percent from West Australian Newspapers
Ltd.
   The acquisition has received formal approval from the Australian
government, Reuters said.
   Reuters supplies a wide range of information services to
business subscribers and the news media.
